arcconf - Command line interface to configure PMC-Sierra
(Microsemi) Controllers.

arcconf_drive_oper.py covers arcconf functionality 
specific to physical and logical drive settings.
 
Note:
    1. supported controllers pci_ids can be entered 
       seperated by ",".
    2. TODO: IMAGEUPDATE, SETPOWER, UNINIT 
    3. Irrepsective of number of disks specified at yaml,
       Script picks only the first two disks for test 
       optimization.
